        <div id="artwork-image">
            <a href="..\/images\/166064_2857906.jpg" class="enlargement-link enlargement-link-110761"><img src="images/166064_2857908.jpg" alt="Venetian Glass Workers" title="John Singer Sargent
American, 1856-1925, Venetian Glass Workers"  /></a>          </div>

    <p class="tools">
              <a href="..\/images\/166064_2857906.jpg" class="enlargement-link enlargement-link-110761"><strong>View</strong> enlargement</a><br />
                          <a href="http://www.artic.edu/aic/collections/exhibitions/American/artwork/110761/email"><strong>Email</strong> to a friend</a><br />
